---
// Toast container - JS controls visibility via classes
---

<div
  id="toast-container"
  class="fixed bottom-4 right-4 z-[100] flex flex-col gap-2 w-80 max-w-[calc(100vw-2rem)] md:bottom-4 md:right-4"
  aria-live="polite"
  aria-atomic="false"
>
  <!-- Toasts are injected here by JS -->
</div>
